					<SHORT-NAME>vSecPrim</SHORT-NAME>
					<DESC>
						<L-2 L="EN">The Software Crypto Library vSecPrim provides cryptographic algorithms and can be used within AUTOSAR or as a standalone library. If it is used within AUTOSAR, the module is only to be used in combination with the Crypto Driver.

#Security #Cryptography #Library
#Vector
						</L-2>
					</DESC>
